name: You Held
description: POV is what your life looks like after the bull run. Only the holders who hold out long enough and are diligent reap the big rewards and become the celebrated memecoin millionaires. POV is #1 hashtag on social media and is used by everyone, everywhere. partnerships with crypto millionaires, crypto influencers or even people in the porn industry are conceivable, as they all use POV. POV in itself is universal, it adds the important crypto addition of you held, as only the right holders reap the rewards.
